{"word":"εὐροκλύδων","slug":"εὐροκλύδων","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>εὐροϰλύδων, ωνος, ὁ</el></b> [<el>εὖρος</el> ‘the east wind’, <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κλύδων\">κλύδων</a></el> ‘surf, rough water’] of a southeast wind called <el>εὐ</el>., <b>southeaster <a href='B:510 27:14'>Ac 27:14</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a></b> Also <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:εὐρυκλύδων\">εὐρυκλύδων</a></el> as <b><a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a></b> in the same <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> The preferred reading is <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:εὐρακύλων\">εὐρακύλων</a></el>, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ q.v.\">q.v.</a> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:εὕροιεν\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:εὐρυκλύδων\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}